reviews.review_text:
NICE SOUND These were the good old days  love the spanish jams.....  fav is from park west 83,this ones a close 2nd.    Why is it no mic for brent here though? I thought it odd at the show itself still wonder after all these years? Anyone know why that was the case.   Has one next night at Gaaaahden sings far from me.
  other highlight was phil chant long before the phil chants.   Kinda like the first not fade scat came during Binghampton in 83.

Great show early on a great tour. I am not gonna write a review or anything close to that all you really need to do is listen the energy is palpable.A nice small place that we would soon find out small venues were few and far between.Do yourself a favor and find that sticky,icky and listen i promise you that you will be glad you did. The show in the cap centre is where we started then maine,boston,nyc,and i think it ended in syracuse.Happy Trails, again you will be glad you made the trip.
